      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-loved and super reliable for all your daily commutes or fun weekend getaways. It runs like a dream and is just waiting for someone new to take the wheel and start some fresh adventures! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by and take it for a spin. Can't wait to hear from you!",
      "price": 32500.0,
