      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a prime example of a well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical signs of careful use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the leather seats show light bolstering wear but remain soft and supportive. All electronics, including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, function exactly as they should. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises, backed by a complete folder of service records showcasing regular oil changes and recent brake pad replacements. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the transmission shifts seamlessly through every gear. This is a reliable, honest car that looks great in a driveway and performs even better on the open road.",
